{"word":"G879 - ἀφυπνόω - aphypnóō - af-oop-no'-o - Fall asleep","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀφυπνόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">aphypnóō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">af-oop-no'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fall asleep</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நித்திரையாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to awaken from sleep"},{"paragraph":"2. to fall asleep, to fall off to sleep"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G5258 - ὕπνος - hýpnos - hoop'-nos/5258\">G5258</a>; properly to <i>become awake</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>drop</i> (off) in slumber: - fall asleep.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1797/1797\">G1797</a>, <a href=\"#/G1798/1798\">G1798</a>, <a href=\"#/G1852/1852\">G1852</a>, <a href=\"#/G1853/1853\">G1853</a>, <a href=\"#/G5258/5258\">G5258</a>, <a href=\"#/G879/879\">G879</a>"}]}